and some fucking sticks.

46:07.517 --> 46:08.727
I've seen you do it enough.

46:09.593 --> 46:12.243
Well, I wish you luck.

46:12.401 --> 46:14.708
And I'll tell you where
to send my last check.

46:15.698 --> 46:17.512
Second coconut tree on the left.

46:19.015 --> 46:20.067
That's a good rock.

46:22.471 --> 46:23.505
Good tree.

46:24.406 --> 46:25.508
Good foundation.

46:28.296 --> 46:29.692
This will be my home.

46:45.996 --> 46:47.147
Now we're cookin'.

47:25.000 --> 47:26.075
Ha!

47:35.436 --> 47:39.419
Oh, mmm. Mmm.

48:16.018 --> 48:17.052
