48:17.513 --> 48:19.066
Hi.

48:23.086 --> 48:24.153
"Hepl"?

48:57.320 --> 48:59.256
Mmm. Mmm.

49:32.901 --> 49:34.095
You're beat.

49:44.600 --> 49:46.876
Hello.

49:49.005 --> 49:50.014
Hello.

49:50.273 --> 49:51.277
Knock, knock.

49:52.027 --> 49:53.058
Hey.

49:53.662 --> 49:54.663
Linda?

49:55.198 --> 49:56.302
- Mmm.
- Is that you?

49:56.592 --> 49:59.051
