-Mr. Preston?

50:04.232 --> 50:05.573
Yeah. That's right. How are you?

50:05.598 --> 50:06.798
I'm great.

50:06.824 --> 50:08.625
Oh, you have
a... something in your...

50:08.650 --> 50:10.233
Mmm.

50:10.593 --> 50:11.680
Oh, dear.

50:14.407 --> 50:15.682
Yeah.

50:16.485 --> 50:18.721
